n Allah that he will enter Paradise, whether he wages jihad in the way of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/former-enemies-embrace-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2973,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Former enemies, prisoners embrace Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah marvels at people who enter Paradise in chains.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3010 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Jawzi said, \u201cIt means they are taken prisoner and detained, but when they recognize the rightness of Islam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17868,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/26\/only-practice-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2973,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Only practicing the pillars of Islam?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A man asked the Prophet, \u201cDo you think if I pray the five prescribed prayers, I fast the month of Ramadan, and I uphold what is lawful and unlawful without adding anything to it, will I enter Paradise?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/27\/essentials-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2973,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Essentials of salvation are pillars of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin\u00a0came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, show me a deed by which I may enter Paradise.\u201d The Prophet said,\u00a0\u201cWorship Allah and never associate anything with Him, establish the prescribed prayers, give the obligatory\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/wife-does-duty-enters-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":2973,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Women: A dutiful wife enters Paradise by any gate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a woman prays her five prayers, fasts her month of Ramadan, guards her chastity, and obeys her husband, she will enter Paradise from any gate she wishes.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4163 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-umar-why-not-go-for-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":2973,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Ibn Umar, why do you not go for jihad?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Tawus reported: A man said to Abdullah ibn Umar, \u201cWhy do you not join the military campaigns?\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: Verily, Islam is built upon five: to testify there is no God but Allah, to establish prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2973","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2973"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2973\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2973"}],"wp:term":[{"